        {
            "title": "中遠集團旗下兩艘貨櫃船再度嘗試通過霍爾木茲海峽駛離波斯灣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 根據彭博新聞匯編的船舶追蹤數據，兩艘與中國國有企業中遠海運集團有關聯的貨櫃船再次嘗試通過<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>駛離波斯灣，而它們幾天前的上一次嘗試無功而返。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據顯示，「中海印度洋」和「中海北冰洋」周一上午從杜拜附近海域向東北方向航行，駛向伊朗拉臘克島和蓋什姆島之間的一條航道，那裡靠近霍爾木茲海峽狹窄的出口。根據隸屬於中遠海運集團的中遠海運貨櫃運輸有限公司的網站信息，這兩艘船均被列為該公司船隊成員。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b1e6374f-4e25-379a-b428-2843ae4e5fbc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為報復美以空襲，伊朗已切斷霍爾木茲海峽這一全球貿易關鍵通道的通行，目前近期只有少數經德黑蘭批准的船隻仍可通過，其中包括液化石油氣運輸船。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"可以看到，「中海印度洋」（白色）和「中海北冰洋」（藍色）正駛向伊朗水域，試圖向東穿越霍爾木茲海峽。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QEp6ve4UEinBClKRItuJ2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/509ec98932d6d4723458d7ed241cc7be\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">可以看到，「中海印度洋」（白色）和「中海北冰洋」（藍色）正駛向伊朗水域，試圖向東穿越霍爾木茲海峽。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩艘船都發出信號，表明船東和船員均為中國背景，顯然意在確保安全通過這條水道。上周五，這兩艘船在伊朗附近掉頭時也採取了同樣的做法。目前尚不清楚，它們當時為何沒有駛離海灣，而是折返回航。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這兩艘貨輪各可運載約1.9萬個20呎標準箱，周一被看到沿著與上次相同的航線航行。自美國和以色列對伊朗發動戰爭以來，它們已在波斯灣滯留一個多月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Two Chinese Container Ships From Cosco Attempt Hormuz Exit Again</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%A0%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%A9%E8%89%98%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E8%88%B9%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%98%97%E8%A9%A6%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E9%A7%9B%E9%9B%A2%E6%B3%A2%E6%96%AF%E7%81%A3-073216916.html",
