        {
            "title": "重慶大廈賓館8年勁蝕8,000萬 投資者6,600萬接貨 租金回報8.7厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0Qws4JgXDZJPtxr.IAZ36Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/78c80d1564ba901c44b59a43a48208a5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由本地投資者何志勇持有的尖沙咀<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"重慶大廈\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:重慶大廈;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/重慶大廈\">重慶大廈</a>一籃子物業，近期以6,600萬元沽出，物業8年賬面跌價5,900萬元，連同使費料實蝕近8,000萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述物業為尖沙咀彌敦道36至44號重慶大廈A座4樓及5樓兩層，原則每層有9個住宅單位，每伙實用面積620至964方呎，現時改裝成設有75間客房的賓館，總樓面面積約18,636方呎，去年中以1.1億元放售，累減4成至約6,600萬元售出，呎價約3,542元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據了解，物業目前月租收入約48萬元，新買家料享租金回報約8.7厘。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-17c3f399-9322-3d8f-9a5c-7871474bd44d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該物業由投資者何志勇在2018年3月以1.25億元購入，呎價6,707元，8年賬面跌價5,900萬元或47.2%，由於買家入市時須付辣稅1,875萬元，連同代理佣金等使費在內，是次沽貨實際或蝕近8,000萬元離場。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重慶大廈位於尖沙咀彌敦道36-44號，毗鄰金域假日酒店，是尖沙咀著名地標。大廈建於1961年，當時建立的目的是為了居住，但現在由平價酒店、商店等服務業使用，匯聚來自亞非各國的商人、勞工和各國的背包旅客。近年不時有遊客於網絡分享入住重慶大廈內賓館中伏的經歷，大廈特殊的氛圍常與已拆除的九龍寨城做對比。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"太子舊樓銀主盤9成業權7,500萬沽 原由波叔家族2.2億收購 七年狂貶66%\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:太子舊樓銀主盤9成業權7,500萬沽 原由波叔家族2.2億收購 七年狂貶66%;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4sLR2HD\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">太子舊樓銀主盤9成業權7,500萬沽 原由波叔家族2.2億收購 七年狂貶66%</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"2\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"波叔家族4,500萬放售旺角旅館 每間房150萬 低市價一成\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:波叔家族4,500萬放售旺角旅館 每間房150萬 低市價一成;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3Mfe0GX\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">波叔家族4,500萬放售旺角旅館 每間房150萬 低市價一成</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"3\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E8%B3%93%E9%A4%A88%E5%B9%B4%E5%8B%81%E8%9D%958-000%E8%90%AC-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%856-600%E8%90%AC%E6%8E%A5%E8%B2%A8-%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B18-7%E5%8E%98-75327\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"4\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
